This product includes software developed as part of the AxiMate project.

AxiMate builds on native open-source components including **Higress**, **HiClaw**,
and **CoPaw** (each stated as Apache License 2.0 upstreams — confirm in each
project’s LICENSE). Runtime containers and installers are provided by those
upstream projects when you deploy via deploy/scripts (HiClaw official installer).
See docs/COMPLIANCE-APACHE2.md and the Software Bill of Materials (SBOM)
published with each release.
